Select trim(A.FormType) as FormType,trim(A.ChartName) as ChartName,(Select trim(SqlCode) From T_SystemAnalystChartManagement Where ChartName = A.ChartName and charttype Not In ('HRuningProjectStatus','HDelayProjectStatus','HAnnualPaymentStatus','HAnnualWorkHourStatus','HRuningTaskStatus') ) as SqlCode,(Select trim(ChartType) From T_SystemAnalystChartManagement Where ChartName = A.ChartName ) as ChartType  From T_SystemAnalystChartRelatedUser A  Where A.UserCode = 'C7094' and A.FormType = 'PersonalSpacePage' and chartName Not In (Select ChartName From T_SystemAnalystChartManagement where ChartType In  ('HRuningProjectStatus','HDelayProjectStatus','HAnnualPaymentStatus','HAnnualWorkHourStatus','HRuningTaskStatus')) Order By A.SortNumber ASC
